original_title: La maquilleuse fait des heures sup'
overview: Rose is a very talented make up artist. She spends her days at a prestigious photo studio where pretty girls come to be "shot' by Bruno, a very famous photographer. The competition is so intense that these girls would do absolutely anything have the best pictures. Their only goal is to be the next covergirls of the biggest fashion magazines.
title: The Make Up Artist Does Extra Hours
